                            <h2 class="mt-4">Problem</h2>
                            <p class="">Singing instructors who teach over <strong>Skype</strong> or <strong>Zoom</strong> sometimes find it difficult to <strong>match</strong> the <strong>effectiveness</strong> of teaching in-person.</p>

                            <p>If we compare an in-person lesson with an online lesson, we're presented with the dilemma of audio lag:</p>

