                            <p>Based on the demo, one can see that, by using the solution, an online lesson is much more similar to an in-person lesson than before. The aformentioned needs of <strong>live accompaniment</strong>, <strong>increased effectiveness</strong>, instructor control of <strong>lesson flow</strong>, and increased <strong>focus on the student</strong> are all achieved.</p>

